{"tid":1438503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場梁先生說出沉默大多數心聲","createTime":"2019-08-09T19:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T11:45:26.000Z","uid":188191,"like":9,"dislike":389,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5712e0b7a8aeaf22a0061756a437be4a3355ba","tid":1438503,"uid":188191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"梁先生雙眼炯炯有神，鏗鏘有力，理直氣狀說出了很多真正香港人的心聲！<br />\n<br />\n好心果班記者，質素低到不堪，作為記者缺乏專業操守，明顯有曬立場，問啲問題又低質，訪問到好似同被訪者嘈交咁唔順氣，好似咩人都可以做記者，可笑！<br />\n<br />\n事實上呢段片反映緊有啲記者影衰曬成個香港傳媒行業！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2425535194391716&amp;id=1649274265351150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2425535194391716%26id%3D1649274265351150&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=926bc138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2425535194391716&amp;id=1649274265351150</a>"},{"pid":"a04f0ee73f6687087aa855dabb873afbffad9bb9","tid":1438503,"uid":274136,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:32:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"92ac53bd03e615c4ce9ed86bba521be0d608c389","tid":1438503,"uid":37232,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:57:44.000Z","msg":"講歪理, 唔覺得佢有理由"},{"pid":"b19710ea4932f12d64aa6cc92aa6a59711b56dd1","tid":1438503,"uid":188191,"like":1,"dislike":57,"score":-56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"梁生仲要比班示威人仕醒左一拳，仍保持冷靜鎮定！"},{"pid":"684dd02b78621783b472de0169b98980b780714b","tid":1438503,"uid":44870,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:00:36.000Z","msg":"先起底, 後回覆, 善用不推文功能"},{"pid":"21ad64fbdf7a963e74a0324a75f4a50bf0bc75d6","tid":1438503,"uid":5627,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMOm2dz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMOm2dz.jpg&h=6477d81b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"677e40a84d037b6b99fffc2d199f57d61d909834","tid":1438503,"uid":188191,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"quote":{"pid":"21ad64fbdf7a963e74a0324a75f4a50bf0bc75d6","tid":1438503,"uid":5627,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMOm2dz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMOm2dz.jpg&h=6477d81b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"應該有好多當日係被罷工，實質無咁多&hellip;"},{"pid":"915954f5c83cb90b871e61b58383e321d8300ad0","tid":1438503,"uid":235458,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:06:41.000Z","msg":"口口聲聲話講事實 但自己咪又係講有500萬人唔反對呢啲未經證實既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bc3bb2ffa09de075929c6d9e809f49e6456d9b","tid":1438503,"uid":280853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:23:12.000Z","msg":"是其是，非其非。<br />\n我地真係不能忘記初心，走歪路。<br />\n當大家因爲黑警濫暴濫權，司法包疪下，向狗屋狗宿舍施襲，無人會怪，社會大眾感到大快人心。<br />\n<br />\n但我地唔可以自我膨脹，唔同意見，想打人就打人。<br />\n咁同紅衛兵同文革無分別。<br />\n<br />\n有些地方要以武制暴，有些地方要有高既公民質素，咁先會贏。<br />\n<br />\n大家要保持熱心，同時冷靜理性，對抗呢個邪惡既港共政權。"},{"pid":"456430b066ab263aa0360e036e06aa23262c1c06","tid":1438503,"uid":188191,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"呢單野就真係要煲大佢啦，比人知道示威者不能接受唔同聲音就打人，仲有比全世界見倒香港記者有幾不堪！"},{"pid":"f42cceb78d015a7a6968a4007fc4e9e3a2ea0afa","tid":1438503,"uid":106929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"915954f5c83cb90b871e61b58383e321d8300ad0","tid":1438503,"uid":235458,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:06:41.000Z","msg":"口口聲聲話講事實 但自己咪又係講有500萬人唔反對呢啲未經證實既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"咁撐警集會 得幾萬人<br />\n咁係咪 600幾萬人 都唔撐警？？？？<br />\n<br />\n自己又話有送中 就出來<br />\n咁即係你自己都反對條法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1508af7648a10158b68c32cdd3058b66634ec391","tid":1438503,"uid":106929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"456430b066ab263aa0360e036e06aa23262c1c06","tid":1438503,"uid":188191,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"呢單野就真係要煲大佢啦，比人知道示威者不能接受唔同聲音就打人，仲有比全世界見倒香港記者有幾不堪！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"咁機場 有一千人 得一個人 打佢<br />\n係咪證明大家都係和平示威者<br />\n<br />\nD被襲者都支持和平示威<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣屈晒佢地都係暴力根本9up"},{"pid":"e663222ff9c7c9249027c9c959b9195a23eb966b","tid":1438503,"uid":120658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"聽佢9Up既人唔好晒時間啦"},{"pid":"99a3a04970a538e93449bfa3d933e32cfe927ade","tid":1438503,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c521ada5bb08bc06ca269afde9109d1af6b2b0d7","tid":1438503,"uid":80301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人知乜事"},